N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7200.9 - Public notice

State Regulations

The commission shall post a notice containing the title and
business address of the records access officer, the persons determining
appeals, and the location where records can be seen or copied, in a conspicuous
location where records are kept. Notes
